[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Sebring Modified [/b]
Week 6 of 12 - 2016 Season 2[/size][/color]
Race Distance: 18 laps, approximately 25 minutes

This week we travel to Florida for the Modified layout of the famous Sebring Raceway. Later in the season we will also visit the Club course. Put together these two make up the International layout, which we will come back to next season (2016 S3).

